<paragraph blockId="112.[151,1436,1664,1727]" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">
The genus was revised by 
<bibRefCitation author="Antoine, Ph. &amp; Camiade, D." box="[448,759,1664,1691]" pageId="112" pageNumber="113" pagination="1 - 8" refId="ref80891" refString="Antoine, Ph. &amp; Camiade, D. (1995) Revision du genre Platygenia MacLeay et description d'une espece nouvelle (Coleoptera, Cetoniidae). Coleopteres, 1 (1), 1 - 8." type="journal article" year="1995">Antoine &amp; Camiade (1995)</bibRefCitation>
, who recognized four valid species. There is one species recorded for 
<collectingCountry box="[272,354,1701,1727]" name="Angola" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">Angola</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Paulino de Oliveira, M." box="[369,656,1701,1727]" pageId="112" pageNumber="113" pagination="40 - 52" refId="ref86751" refString="Paulino de Oliveira, M. (1882) Etudes sur les insectes d'Angola qui se trouvent au Museum National de Lisbonne. Jornal de Sciencias Mathematicas Physicas e Naturaes, 33, 40 - 52." type="journal article" year="1882">Paulino de Oliveira 1882</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
